result.name: McDonald's

reviews.text: Shittiest MCD you can find. Huge queues and there is literally only one person actually working. He is working hard. Taking orders. Filming them but the line doesn’t move. Three Registers are empty and several employees and standing around in the back. No one bothers to help out

This happen in Cameron road @Hongkong. Wow! The Angus burger is very good delicious. Taste like a real hamburger back in America. Definitely, we will eat it again. You must try in if anyone can visit there.

We ate here for breakfast when we did not want to spend a whole lot of money. This McDonald's offers the normal menu of McDonald's with other Chinese dishes available. Does McDonald's only has dine-in or take-out due to its location. It also has long bench seating in the middle so you may be sitting with others if you eat here.

It's a busy McDonald's at midnight on a Friday, but despite the high turnover, they managed delivery dried out burgers that seemed to be sitting in tray for a long time and cold French fries.

Usually when you see high turnover at a fast food restaurant, you can expect the food to be freshly cooked. But for some reason that wasn't so here, and the entire experience was lacking because of it.

Adequate seating, 24 hour operation and good location are saving graces, yet still I don't feel that I can recommend this McD with 3 others and 2 KFCs within walking distance.

NOT RECOMMEND.
It was McDonald's you know what you are getting.

result.name: 麥當勞

reviews.text: 尖沙咀店麥當勞服務員態度很不佳，且叫餐講很小聲，最最最重要的是工作人員都在抓頭髮撥頭髮，環境衛生跟街道很像，薯餅超級油，升級港式奶茶等於降等級，飲料裝七分很扯，很難相信人的服務品質能好到哪？都不能打零顆星。不然一定打零分。
跟其他麥當奴一樣，毫無特式!
地方細，冇自助機，傳統落單方式，都唔知邊份餐係自己
